   Aztar Corp. Unit's Redemption
</HL>
<DATE>
09/24/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   AZTR
</CO>
<IN>
CASINOS AND GAMBLING (CNO)
BUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK)
</IN>
<LP>
   PHOENIX, Ariz. -- Aztar Corp. said its Ramada New Jersey
Holdings Corp. unit intends to redeem its 459,000 outstanding
shares of convertible Class A preferred stock at $9 a share,
the maximum allowed under the company's certificate of
incorporation.
   The redemption will be effective as of Jan. 4, 1991, the
gambling concern said.
</LP>
